WEBVTT

00:00.470 --> 00:07.470
I bow to

00:49.580 --> 00:56.580
all the seekers of truth. I’ve been many
a times in Birmingham before and today I find

03:42.260 --> 03:49.260
there are so many people whom I know very
well, and gradually we are all increasing

03:53.209 --> 03:57.709
in size, understanding our Spirit.

03:57.709 --> 04:04.709
Now, the seeking of the Spirit is not a new
thing. It’s a very ancient pursuit of human

04:10.530 --> 04:17.530
beings. They have been seeking the Spirit
and many a times many prophets, many great

04:22.810 --> 04:29.810
incarnations came on this Earth to help the
people in their pursuit. The seeking of the

04:36.520 --> 04:43.520
Spirit is a inner urge, a very compelling
urge within ourselves. But we don’t know

04:48.669 --> 04:55.669
what we have to seek; we don’t know what
it means to be twice born.

05:03.300 --> 05:10.300
I come from India and suddenly I feel I belong
to Britain. I’ve become British and I feel

05:21.030 --> 05:28.030
the shock that we are all facing. Where are
we going? The other day I saw some program

05:35.590 --> 05:42.590
about cocaine smuggling in England and I was
shocked. All self-destructive things sometimes

05:52.290 --> 05:57.500
can be misunderstood as Spirit seeking. One
can misunderstand. But they lead us nowhere

05:57.500 --> 06:04.500
- is a fact. Then why do we do it? We do it
- I know that we do it only because we are

06:21.639 --> 06:28.639
seeking the Spirit. It’s very misleading,
though. We seek the Spirit in wrong things.

06:30.350 --> 06:37.350
This urge we think will be fulfilled by wrong
things, by doing wrong to ourselves, by harming

06:41.070 --> 06:44.009
ourselves, by torturing ourselves.

06:44.009 --> 06:51.009
We get bored. Why? Why do we get bored of
life? Life should be bubbling with joy. Because

06:55.210 --> 07:02.180
we think life is worth nothing, we have to
seek. And what do we seek there? It’s a

07:02.180 --> 07:09.180
amazing thing how many seekers are born in
the West – so many seekers! Even I talk

07:14.930 --> 07:21.930
to little children and I am surprised that
there is seeking within them. They are seeking

07:24.180 --> 07:31.180
something and they don’t understand the
mystery of seeking. They don’t even understand

07:36.440 --> 07:43.199
what they are seeking, but they think there’s
something wrong. They feel frustrated, angered,

07:43.199 --> 07:49.000
and they feel that life has not given them
what they wanted. They’re bored stiff; they

07:49.000 --> 07:56.000
don’t know what to do so they take to vandalism,
some sort of a sensation. They try to destroy

07:56.590 --> 08:02.849
others or themselves.

08:02.849 --> 08:09.849
So the human mind today is at a different
level, we must understand, especially in the

08:12.470 --> 08:16.910
West. Of course East has its own problems,
but it has traditional understanding about

08:16.910 --> 08:23.910
seeking and it understands what to seek. But
in the West such intense seekers are there

08:25.400 --> 08:32.400
and they don’t know what to seek, what to
achieve, what is Spirit. It’s a big problem.

08:33.349 --> 08:40.349
But today one has to realize that the category
of people that are born in these modern times

08:43.259 --> 08:50.259
are very different from the people who were
born about say, I would say fifty years back.

08:51.149 --> 08:58.149
They had political ambitions, economic ambitions;
they wanted to achieve political freedom,

09:01.759 --> 09:08.759
power. That generation is practically over
now. They have realized that in this power

09:11.040 --> 09:18.040
game they’re not going to gain anything.
It’s a subject finished now for them; it’s

09:18.679 --> 09:25.679
something absurd. They find the whole thing
is a joke - same with the economic problem.

09:25.769 --> 09:32.769
Like there was once upon a time a gold rush.
So everybody rushed to find the gold. Today

09:34.589 --> 09:41.589
if anybody wants to do that, people will think,
“Are you mad? Must be joking.”

09:43.100 --> 09:50.100
So the category of people today are of a different
level, we must be aware of that. We must understand

09:51.600 --> 09:57.929
that the category is very different which
perhaps media people don’t understand so

09:57.929 --> 10:04.540
much. I don’t think they have any idea as
to what is the level of awareness of human

10:04.540 --> 10:11.540
beings today in the West. They are still of
that old school which was busy fighting elections

10:12.860 --> 10:19.860
or strikes and this and that - all nonsensical
things. But the people who are aware are many,

10:24.689 --> 10:31.689
many more than yet what we know of, that they
are seeking something very different that

10:33.529 --> 10:40.529
their fathers and forefathers did not seek,
because the times are such. Today, it’s

10:40.949 --> 10:47.949
a special time – special time where many
people have to get their Spirit. But then

10:49.739 --> 10:56.739
again we are misled because people who are
trying to exploit this have found a good market,

11:01.040 --> 11:08.040
and they come down to find out how they can
market their goods in this new awareness of

11:11.910 --> 11:13.389
people.

11:13.389 --> 11:20.389
We get enamored because we are still not fully
conscious or knowledgeable about what to expect

11:24.449 --> 11:31.449
in your spiritual pursuit. And that’s how
they come and befool us. We have cults and

11:32.239 --> 11:39.239
we have sects, but one must understand that
as you have grown through amoeba in your evolutionary

11:43.059 --> 11:50.059
process, gradually, from that to this level,
the awareness has to also grow the same way,

11:51.809 --> 11:58.259
in a traditional way. It cannot be somebody
like Freud coming up and saying something

11:58.259 --> 12:05.259
new, that we accept. Suddenly, how can we
deviate from all those who talked of something

12:10.459 --> 12:17.459
very different from what Freud has been talking?
Because it’s a mind which is of course very

12:19.660 --> 12:26.660
aware, but also it is what we call very right-sided
mind, as is described in the Gita they are

12:27.189 --> 12:34.189
called as the people who are rajasikas, the
people who are in action. They live with the

12:37.019 --> 12:40.480
power of action.

12:40.480 --> 12:47.480
So the people who live with the power of their
action live with their egos, and ego likes

12:48.569 --> 12:54.709
something new, some sort of a new stuff comes
in they think, “Oh, why not do that? Try

12:54.709 --> 13:01.709
this, try that.” It’s like a horse which
wants to go into every new direction and fails.

13:05.449 --> 13:12.449
It’s a very venturesome horse, I think,
and that’s how something new somebody says,

13:13.959 --> 13:20.959
everybody jumps to it. We are not new ourselves,
we are ancient. And when we take to some new

13:25.489 --> 13:32.489
idea suddenly we find after some time that
we have to recoil back, because these are

13:34.569 --> 13:41.569
all mental projections and that’s how in
every religion there have been sects formed.

13:42.609 --> 13:49.609
Because, say Catholicism - Martin Luther who
was himself a realized soul saw that Pope

13:52.379 --> 13:59.379
was doing all kinds of wrong things, so he
started a new sect. But it’s a mental projection

13:59.449 --> 14:06.449
still, I would say, though he was a realized
soul. Then out of that came out I don’t

14:07.689 --> 14:13.079
know how many churches. So now we have one
Unification Church which turned out to be

14:13.079 --> 14:19.029
another horrible stuff, then we have Unity
Church where they unite all these sects – is

14:19.029 --> 14:26.029
all projections, all branches of that mental
movement. But the essence is lost. In the

14:28.859 --> 14:35.859
first case it was lost, and it was completely
forgotten in the last case.

14:38.209 --> 14:45.009
So that’s how the sects were born. Now we
find Pentecostals. The other day I was reading

14:45.009 --> 14:52.009
the harm it has done to people. We have all
kinds of faiths - Seventh Day Adventists.

14:52.419 --> 14:59.419
What does it matter what was the seventh day,
the Sabbath? Supposing you have your Sabbath

15:00.259 --> 15:07.259
day, say, on the seventh day, will you become
righteous? Will you become virtuous? Will

15:09.220 --> 15:16.220
you become your Spirit? By changing a particular
type of ideology or thought, will you be transformed,

15:31.720 --> 15:38.529
will you become great, will you become a super
human being? No. Then what? You think that

15:38.529 --> 15:43.129
by going from one sect to another sect you’ll
achieve something great, you will just form

15:43.129 --> 15:50.129
different social orders, that’s all.

15:50.379 --> 15:57.379
Then you have anti-culture, another sect formed
as a reaction. That also is another problem.

15:59.579 --> 16:06.439
All these venturesome ideas of this horse
takes you from places to places, and you think,

16:06.439 --> 16:11.600
“Why whenever we try to do something why
we are committing the mistake?” Because

16:11.600 --> 16:18.600
we have forgotten the fundamental, and the
fundamental is very simple, that you have

16:20.379 --> 16:27.379
to seek your Spirit, and when you seek your
Spirit it is a spontaneous happening, it’s

16:28.139 --> 16:35.139
a living process in your evolutionary process
by which you become the Spirit. By mental

16:37.160 --> 16:39.739
projection you cannot.

16:39.739 --> 16:46.739
Then the people who took advantage of the
situation that there are so many seekers on

16:47.889 --> 16:54.889
this Earth, they started all kinds of cults,
also. I’ve been talking against them since

16:58.389 --> 17:05.389
1970 that “Don’t go to these cults. These
are another ego-pampering stuffs.” Suddenly

17:07.199 --> 17:14.199
they start a new idea – it appeals to you.
Suddenly someone says that “No, by leading

17:14.819 --> 17:21.819
this kind of a life you’ll achieve God.”
You accept it. Why not find out? Since ages

17:23.669 --> 17:30.669
people have been writing about the spiritual
life. What does that mean? How to achieve

17:32.340 --> 17:39.340
it? Why do you take to anyone who just says
that “This is so, this is so”? Because

17:40.370 --> 17:47.370
perhaps they have a nice circus or a publicity.
There must be something that is so attractive

17:51.919 --> 17:57.970
that people take to it. Or maybe it is some
sort of a ego-pampering that you want to join

17:57.970 --> 18:01.419
these cults and get destroyed.

18:01.419 --> 18:08.419
There cannot be a cult for your assent. What
cults did you follow to become human beings?

18:14.710 --> 18:21.710
The nature itself works it out. It is a spontaneous
happening. But for a person who lives only

18:23.990 --> 18:28.960
with mental projections, morning till evening
you see television or listen to radio, it’s

18:28.960 --> 18:33.720
nothing but mental projection all the time,
you see, hovering on your head. You cannot

18:33.720 --> 18:39.139
think that there is something beyond that
mental projection which is the reality.

18:39.139 --> 18:46.139
So you find reality horrifying, absolutely
horrifying. You have to pay the tax; you have

18:47.559 --> 18:51.059
to pay the rates; you have to pay this. You
have to be like this; you have to be dressed

18:51.059 --> 18:57.029
up like this; you have to have clothes like
this. All kinds of pressures on your head.

18:57.029 --> 19:03.389
So now what to do? How to get out of this?
This is reality for people.

19:03.389 --> 19:10.389
So then we accept the drugs and the alcohols
and things because we want to get out of it.

19:13.539 --> 19:20.539
That gives definitely a sensation, hallucination;
but reality in itself is so beautiful, is

19:24.909 --> 19:31.909
so surmounting all this, that we have to honestly
understand that if it is reality, it cannot

19:36.679 --> 19:43.679
be hallucination. It cannot. You cannot pay
for it. You cannot follow somebody who says

19:45.389 --> 19:52.389
something against the tradition of evolution.
It has to be fundamental, what it has been

20:00.950 --> 20:07.950
and will be. It has to be something that is
integrating everything, integrating all the

20:09.240 --> 20:14.710
religions, integrating all the religious leaders,
all the great prophets and all the great incarnations,

20:14.710 --> 20:21.710
otherwise it cannot be reality because reality
has to be one. It should unite everything.

20:24.830 --> 20:31.830
It cannot create a separate identity on mental
level. It may create on a spiritual level,

20:37.700 --> 20:44.700
maybe, that people who get Realization, who
have got Self Realization, maybe the people

20:47.519 --> 20:54.519
form a more coordinated concord among themselves,
but they’re all the time worried about the

20:58.789 --> 21:05.789
other people who are not yet in there – not
for money, not for lust, not for greed, but

21:06.330 --> 21:13.330
only because they want to share the joy of
reality.

21:14.279 --> 21:20.230
This has to be first of all understood by
all those who are seeking that reality cannot

21:20.230 --> 21:27.230
be a mental projection, neither can it be
a emotional projection which we can manage

21:28.379 --> 21:33.330
ourselves. One moment we are in love, another
moment we are walking to the divorce cases.

21:33.330 --> 21:40.330
Why? If there was some truth in that kind
of a love, why? It is something beyond, which

21:42.009 --> 21:49.009
is eternal, which doesn’t change, which
overflows, is promised. What about that? Why

21:51.169 --> 21:53.620
not seek that?

21:53.620 --> 22:00.620
Then you turn your eyes to find out where
it is described. Vedas were written thousand

22:05.279 --> 22:12.279
of years back and every Veda, whichever you
read, the Upanishads as they are called as

22:15.149 --> 22:22.149
the people where they have described about
human beings have talked that you have to

22:23.320 --> 22:30.320
worry about your Spirit, it’s the Spirit
that is important. Then you have other people,

22:32.269 --> 22:37.639
in India we had fourteen thousand years back
some great poets. All of them have said the

22:37.639 --> 22:44.639
same. Then we have people in other countries
like Abraham, like Moses, we have Confucius,

22:51.389 --> 22:58.389
Lao Tse. We have Krishna, Rama. All of them
have said one thing, and one thing that “You

23:02.450 --> 23:05.750
seek your Spirit.”

23:05.750 --> 23:12.750
If so, then how? We should again look back.
It is described how to seek it. It is described

23:20.710 --> 23:27.710
in Gita, but much before that it is described
in the Vedas very clearly about the Kundalini

23:29.129 --> 23:36.129
and the seven Chakras. Nobody says in any
book that when the Kundalini awakens you become

23:36.860 --> 23:42.970
mad or you start jumping like a frog.

23:42.970 --> 23:49.970
Recently I went to Pune, and there I was surprised
that the Brahmins of Pune, who are supposed

23:50.350 --> 23:57.350
to be very learned people, were all suffering
from high blood pressure, from kidney troubles,

23:58.110 --> 24:05.110
from insanity. I mean name any disease, they
had it. I said, “Why are they suffering

24:06.120 --> 24:09.899
like this?” So there was one fellow called
[Gumani, Gurumani, or Gulumani ???] Maharaj

24:09.899 --> 24:15.629
who really came as the killer of all these
Brahmins, I think, that they followed him.

24:15.629 --> 24:22.629
And their main person came to discuss with
Me about his religion, so-called.

24:24.440 --> 24:29.049
And he started asking Me, “Do you know about
“terno pai, erno pai”

24:29.049 --> 24:36.049
I said, “What is that? I’ve never heard.
Where is it described?”

24:37.190 --> 24:39.200
‘Oh, You have never heard about it?”

24:39.200 --> 24:39.860
I said, “No.”

24:39.860 --> 24:41.409
“Do You know about shaktipath?”

24:41.409 --> 24:47.090
I said, “I’ve never heard about this.
From where does it come? Which book?”

24:47.090 --> 24:48.509
“Oh, it’s from one book.”

24:48.509 --> 24:49.990
I said, “Which book?”

24:49.990 --> 24:55.690
“About sixty years back there was one Vishnutirth,
Swami Vishnutirth who wrote this book.”

24:55.690 --> 24:57.279
I said, “Really?”

24:57.279 --> 25:02.330
He’s the only one. Only sixty years back
this fellow comes up from somewhere, writes

25:02.330 --> 25:08.809
down something new, “erno pai, terno pai.”
All the Vedas, all the Shastras are all finished.

25:08.809 --> 25:13.460
Bible is finished. Everything is finished.
Only this fellow sixty years back comes up

25:13.460 --> 25:19.309
from somewhere and talks about shaktipath
and you believe it. All of you, the Brahmins,

25:19.309 --> 25:21.440
the educated, the learned.

25:21.440 --> 25:28.440
I said, “Where do you see these words in
the Vedas? Show Me. Where do you see them

25:28.549 --> 25:29.850
in the Patanjali Yoga Shastra? Show Me. Is
it written anywhere? “

25:29.850 --> 25:30.710
He said, “We haven’t read them.”

25:30.710 --> 25:31.639
I said, “What did you read?”

25:31.639 --> 25:32.450
“This Vishnutirtha’s book.”

25:32.450 --> 25:39.450
I said, “You are supposed to be learned
people in Sanskit. You read only this Vishnutirth

25:39.450 --> 25:42.610
who came only sixty years back?”

25:42.610 --> 25:49.610
How can it be? And all of them are so sick
you won’t believe it, and in My presence

25:53.899 --> 25:59.669
when they came they were in a very bad shape,
absolutely in a very bad shape as if they

25:59.669 --> 26:05.389
had taken cocaine or something worse than
that. Eyes were going up, their hands were

26:05.389 --> 26:08.720
moving like this, all kinds of things.

26:08.720 --> 26:12.950
And I told them, “Please forgive Me. Go
to Vishnutirth or to his disciple, this [Gumani,

26:12.950 --> 26:13.200
Gurumani, or Gulumani ???] Maharaj.”

26:12.950 --> 26:19.950
And the only thing they did was not to eat
this, not to eat that, not to have relationship

26:22.759 --> 26:29.759
with your wife, become like a dry bean, live
on a shoe string and then you become godly,

26:34.440 --> 26:39.499
is it? It’s very simple. In India so many
are like that already.

26:39.499 --> 26:46.499
Use your brains! They are very brainy people.

26:46.559 --> 26:51.820
I said, “How could this man dominate you?”

26:51.820 --> 26:57.340
So they came out with very intelligent answer
that “In the Vedas, you see, when we followed

26:57.340 --> 27:00.799
the Vedas and what did we get?”

27:00.799 --> 27:05.570
“All right.” I said, “You didn’t get
anything. But there’s something promised

27:05.570 --> 27:11.370
in the Vedas, in the ancient books, that in
Kali Yuga, at these modern times, you will

27:11.370 --> 27:17.120
get your Realization. Why didn’t you go
for that?”

27:17.120 --> 27:23.559
But this fellow says that through erno pai,
karuno pai - God knows all kinds of nonsensical

27:23.559 --> 27:30.330
words, it has no meaning at all in Sanskrit
language - that you will get your Realization.

27:30.330 --> 27:36.460
All right, anybody says so, must you join
him? You should have asked, “How do you

27:36.460 --> 27:38.549
get these words? From where did you find them?”

27:38.549 --> 27:43.690
You should have asked Mr. Freud, “From where
do you get your knowledge?” He, himself,

27:43.690 --> 27:49.519
was a drug addict. He, himself, was a horrible
man. He had bad relations with his mother.

27:49.519 --> 27:56.519
He had a cancer, and he becomes your guru
instead of Christ? Suddenly, and you accept

27:58.129 --> 27:58.769
him.

27:58.769 --> 28:05.769
Those people who deal on mental level cannot
talk of God. They cannot understand God. God

28:07.999 --> 28:14.999
can be only understood through your Spirit.
Like your theologians here – theologians

28:15.540 --> 28:22.540
– what do they understand about Christ?
They haven’t got power to talk about Christ.

28:26.899 --> 28:33.179
Just because they are elected, they are just
paid servants of the people to look after

28:33.179 --> 28:40.019
the churches, that’s all. They don’t deserve
to be saints. Why are they so important? At

28:40.019 --> 28:47.019
least in India nobody treats them as something
great. They are just priests, finished.

28:47.580 --> 28:54.580
You have to be a saint to understand God.
You have to be a realized soul to understand

28:55.759 --> 29:02.759
His miracles. You cannot just become a theologian
in a theology school or somewhere and start

29:04.249 --> 29:11.249
talking about God. It’s blasphemous the
way these people talk about God and Christ.

29:14.990 --> 29:19.909
I don’t know how you tolerate it. In India
they would have been stoned and finished long

29:19.909 --> 29:26.909
time back. They don’t know what God is,
how can they know about Christ? It has been

29:30.220 --> 29:36.590
on and on from this Augustine time and this
Paul also another horrid fellow. I don’t

29:36.590 --> 29:43.590
know how they call him as Christian, from
where he becomes Christian. And that now they

29:43.629 --> 29:49.110
are not following Christ, they are following
Paul.

29:49.110 --> 29:56.110
Theologians, intellectuals cannot understand
God. He’s beyond your limited intellect;

29:56.860 --> 30:02.869
He’s an unlimited personality. You have
to jump into that. With your limited knowledge

30:02.869 --> 30:09.869
you can play your horses of your politics,
not of God. Such arrogance, such ego! You

30:13.779 --> 30:20.779
are challenging the wrath of God on your countries
when you go about like this.

30:21.879 --> 30:28.879
Please humble down yourself and understand
that God is beyond your petty intellect. First

30:29.659 --> 30:36.659
become your Spirit. You have to become your
Spirit. By reading if you understand God,

30:43.299 --> 30:50.299
then he’s not God. It’s clearly said “Atmanave
Atmana Tattwa”. You see, through the Spirit

30:51.610 --> 30:58.610
you will know God. Christ has said it so clearly
to Nicodemas that “You are to be born of

30:59.440 --> 31:04.090
the Holy Ghost.” And Who is the Holy Ghost?
These people who go to theological colleges,

31:04.090 --> 31:11.090
are they Holy Ghosts or what are they? They
are nothing but ghosts of intellect.

31:11.850 --> 31:18.850
Beware of them. This is another very subtle
attack on reality. And they all will have

31:20.989 --> 31:27.989
to suffer for it, they must understand. You,
those who are seeking, should seek your Spirit

31:31.230 --> 31:38.230
and should understand that you are invited
in the Kingdom of God. The time has come;

31:38.379 --> 31:45.379
this is the judgment time. This is the judgment
and you can see it so clearly.

31:48.929 --> 31:55.929
So there is attack on the seekers. One, from
ignorance because they don’t know what to

31:56.639 --> 32:03.639
seek, how to seek, what to expect; and there
is attack also from outside because they think

32:06.629 --> 32:13.629
you are ignorant, because they think they
know more than what you know. They don’t

32:15.169 --> 32:22.169
know anything about Christ, believe Me - Who
He was, why He came on this Earth, and how

32:24.559 --> 32:31.559
He plays His role so perfectly within ourselves.

32:31.720 --> 32:38.720
I would request you all to receive your Realization
first. There’s no argument about it; there’s

32:40.049 --> 32:47.049
no discussion about it. Even if you try to
argue it out – I may be able to answer you,

32:48.100 --> 32:54.799
but that won’t give you your Realization,
your Kundalini has to rise. Humble down in

32:54.799 --> 32:56.669
your heart.

32:56.669 --> 33:03.669
I went to a village where about three thousand
people came from all hills of Himalayas, very

33:10.659 --> 33:15.419
simple people. And they were waiting for this.

33:15.419 --> 33:20.379
I asked them, “How is it you were waiting?”

33:20.379 --> 33:27.379
“Oh, it is said. It’s said it, that Devi
Jagaran will be there in modern times. We

33:28.710 --> 33:34.759
were waiting for You to come, Mother. Devi
Jagaran is the awakening of the Goddess, of

33:34.759 --> 33:36.309
the Kundalini.

33:36.309 --> 33:43.309
The villages know about it. On the foothill
of Himalayas they are waiting. In one day

33:44.320 --> 33:49.110
I got three thousand people realized. In this
Birmingham, how many people there are today

33:49.110 --> 33:54.239
who are new, who have come to receive their
Realization? Very few. But theologians get

33:54.239 --> 33:59.200
all these lectures. They like to play with
their mental projections.

33:59.200 --> 34:06.200
But beware, time is very short. Better get
your Realization. Become the Spirit and then

34:10.720 --> 34:17.720
you will know that God is not intellect, It
is love. And love which is not limited – unlimited

34:18.770 --> 34:25.770
love which is the most powerful thing in this
universe which you can become aware of and

34:34.970 --> 34:41.889
you can become empowered with that great,
unlimited love which just flows, acts, coordinates,

34:41.889 --> 34:46.869
thinks, plans, works out everything. This
All-Pervading Power about which you have heard,

34:46.869 --> 34:53.869
you have to know That and get It. You can’t
pay for It. You can’t organize It. It has

34:58.700 --> 35:05.700
to work out like a living process within you.

35:09.369 --> 35:14.109
May God bless you.

