take ice. It is very cold water.]

35:39.569 --> 35:46.569
Come along, come forward. There are lots of
seats here. Who are sitting at the back, come

35:51.670 --> 35:54.040
along. Sit at here.

35:54.040 --> 36:01.040
Can you hear Me? Is it all right? Have you
any questions? Come along, this side. There’s

36:08.020 --> 36:15.020
room this side. Don’t sit on the ground.
There’s room here this side. Any questions?

36:33.099 --> 36:40.099
Question: A man asks if it helps to be a vegetarian.

36:46.780 --> 36:53.780
Shri Mataji: No, no. It has nothing to do
with vegetarianism or not. Christ was not

36:55.270 --> 36:57.569
a vegetarian. It’s all absurdity. Of course
you have to eat whatever suits you. I would

36:57.569 --> 37:04.569
say that – whatever suits you. This vegetarianism
is a fad. It’s just a fad. To believe that

37:06.950 --> 37:13.950
by eating some food you’ll go to God is
a wrong idea. But, of course, alcohol goes

37:16.210 --> 37:20.869
against your awareness, you know that. But
I don’t say, “Don’t take alcohol.”

37:20.869 --> 37:26.410
You will just not take it, that’s all, because
you get the alcohol of God within you and

37:26.410 --> 37:30.010
then you don’t want to take it. That’s
a different point. But I won’t say just

37:30.010 --> 37:31.440
now that “Don’t take it.”

37:31.440 --> 37:38.190
But food has to be seen whatever’s suitable
for your body. I would say that Indians should

37:38.190 --> 37:42.369
take to meat. It would be better. And the
Western people should take to vegetables,

37:42.369 --> 37:49.369
it would be better for them, just to balance.

37:55.450 --> 38:02.450
Question: How do you become your Spirit?

38:16.020 --> 38:23.020
Shri Mataji: That’s a very good question.
That’s the question is - I’m saying it

38:35.200 --> 38:41.490
is a spontaneous happening and that within
us is placed, if you see here in the triangular

38:41.490 --> 38:48.490
bone, is the power of Holy Ghost within us,
which we call in Sanskit language as Kundalini.

38:49.460 --> 38:56.460
In Koran it is called as Assas. In every scripture
it is described. And this Kundalini has to

38:59.890 --> 39:06.890
rise, this power which is the desire power,
which is the pure desire power, because all

39:09.119 --> 39:14.920
other desires are not pure. If they were pure,
then you would have been satisfied. But you’re

39:14.920 --> 39:16.750
not satisfied.

39:16.750 --> 39:23.750
So this pure desire is the desire to become
one with the Spirit. And this is within you,

39:24.690 --> 39:31.230
this force is within you dormantly placed
in the triangular bone called as sacrum. That

39:31.230 --> 39:38.230
means the Greeks also knew the word sacrum
means “sacred.” And this power has to

39:39.319 --> 39:46.319
rise within you, and there are subtle centers
above it, six centers above and one center

39:46.770 --> 39:53.770
below through which it pierces and you feel
the Holy Ghost, which is described by Christ

39:54.770 --> 40:01.770
and you feel the Cool Breeze of the Holy Ghost
coming out of your fontanel bone area which

40:02.200 --> 40:09.200
is the real baptism. And as a result of that
you start feeling your Spirit in your consciousness,

40:16.280 --> 40:21.710
means in your central nervous system. You,
yourself, feel it.

40:21.710 --> 40:28.710
That’s how you become the Spirit. That’s
the only way it is sprouted. It’s a living

40:35.049 --> 40:42.049
process like if you want to sprout a seed,
you have to embed it into this Mother Earth

40:45.349 --> 40:51.690
and spontaneously with the power what Mother
Earth has, it sprouts. In the same way it

40:51.690 --> 40:58.690
happens, and that’s how I have to work it
out. But later on when you get it and you

40:59.619 --> 41:03.480
become established, you can do it yourself
to others. Like one enlightened light can

41:03.480 --> 41:10.480
enlighten another light. But the first light
has to be enlightened.

41:11.230 --> 41:18.230
For that you can get some books from here,
but once you start reading books also I find

41:18.849 --> 41:25.710
you become more bookish, so it’s better
to postpone the reading for some time. Better

41:25.710 --> 41:32.150
get your Realization first. Like I would say
that when you want to put lights on you say,

41:32.150 --> 41:36.380
“All right, switch on.” It’s all built
in there; it’s all done. Only thing you

41:36.380 --> 41:43.380
have to switch on. And the whole thing becomes
enlightened. But I could first of all tell

41:44.000 --> 41:50.200
you all the details about the history of electricity,
then all the organization that has worked

41:50.200 --> 41:57.200
it out - would be a headache. Better have
your light first.

41:58.890 --> 42:05.890
And then you’ll know all about it. And this
is not I’m saying that is today. Has been

42:10.030 --> 42:17.030
said for thousands of years. That is how we
become the Spirit. Christ didn’t tell us

42:18.069 --> 42:25.069
lies when He said that “You are to be born
of the Holy Ghost.”

42:26.240 --> 42:31.400
He never said that any priest can put his
hand on your head and say, “Now you are

42:31.400 --> 42:38.400
a Christian.” Did He say so? He did not.
That’s all artificial. That’s why children

42:40.250 --> 42:47.130
cry such a lot when they’re baptized, I
think. Like William Blake has said that “A

42:47.130 --> 42:49.220
priest cursed me on my head.”

42:49.220 --> 42:56.220
Any other question, please?

43:09.640 --> 43:16.640
Now we have to work it out. It’s very simple
and it will work out in no time. It works

43:31.750 --> 43:38.750
out. It will happen to you in no time but
the problem is, it’s a new experience and

43:43.230 --> 43:50.230
people actually think that when you get an
experience you must jump or you should become

43:52.190 --> 43:57.859
like a mad person. I don’t know what things
are expected.

43:57.859 --> 44:04.859
You become empowered, and unless and until
you use this power how will you know you’re

44:05.480 --> 44:11.559
empowered or not? So to establish that power
you take some time. Once you have established

44:11.559 --> 44:18.559
that power then you can see yourself how you
are blessed, that how this power is flowing

44:20.650 --> 44:27.650
through you of God’s compassion, that how
you are blessed in every way and how you,

44:31.230 --> 44:38.230
yourself, become the source of joy – to
yourself and to others. How you jump into

44:38.349 --> 44:44.740
a new awareness of collective consciousness
by which you can feel the problems of others

44:44.740 --> 44:50.549
and your own problems, how you can cure your
problems and cure the problems of others.

44:50.549 --> 44:57.549
For this you have to have patience with yourself
for a little while and once you’re established

44:58.809 --> 45:05.809
you will see that you, yourself, become your
own master, your own guru.

45:09.910 --> 45:16.910
So to achieve it, we have to do few things
is to understand that we have to have, first

45:22.020 --> 45:29.020
of all, desire. You and your freedom cannot
be challenged. So you have to have intense

45:30.740 --> 45:37.740
desire to be the Spirit. If you have that
desire in your heart, it works much faster.

45:39.470 --> 45:46.470
To express that symbolically we put the left
hand like this which represents the power

45:47.420 --> 45:54.400
of desire and the right hand is the power
of action. We have to take out our shoes because

45:54.400 --> 45:55.839
the Mother Earth helps us a lot. We have to
take out our shoes to take some help from

45:55.839 --> 45:56.089
Mother Earth. Thank God here it’s not concrete,
slightly better than that.

45:55.839 --> 45:56.950
To put both the feet on the Mother Earth in
a parallel manner, and be comfortable - you

45:56.950 --> 45:57.200
have to be comfortable. Now supposing somebody
is feeling uncomfortable because of something

45:57.170 --> 45:59.760
that’s tight on the neck or on the waist,
please loosen it a little bit if you find

45:59.760 --> 46:00.520
that. But if you’re comfortable, it’s
all right. Or somebody has got a coat which

46:00.520 --> 46:00.980
is making one uncomfortable, you can take
it out.

46:00.980 --> 46:02.849
Attention should not be distracted towards
some discomfort to the body. That is important.

46:02.849 --> 46:09.849
Secondly, if you can take out your spectacles
will be better because here you don’t have

46:11.180 --> 46:17.240
to see anything, you have to keep your eyes
shut.

46:17.240 --> 46:22.250
So please put both your feet on the Mother
Earth, your left hand towards Me like this,

46:22.250 --> 46:22.500
with the desire in the mind that we have to
be the Spirit. We are not yet complete till

46:22.280 --> 46:22.530
we become the Spirit; we are not complete
to understand God Who is absolutely complete.

46:22.299 --> 46:24.170
Now the right hand is to be used for the action.
That is on the different centers we have certain

46:24.170 --> 46:26.780
problems. In a village I don’t have to do
all this. You’ll be surprised, it’s just

46:26.780 --> 46:27.130
like this, (Shri Mataji clicks Her fingers)
just like that. I don’t have to do anything

46:27.130 --> 46:27.420
whatsoever. But we are little complicated
so doesn’t’ matter. We have to remove

46:27.420 --> 46:27.730
our own hurdles by putting our hands into
different things. [Shri Mataji speaks aside

46:27.730 --> 46:28.760
in Hindi] Please put your shoes at the back.
Now, you have to keep your eyes shut, but

46:28.760 --> 46:29.880
before that I’ll tell you the different
centers we’ll try to clear out. One is on

46:29.880 --> 46:30.650
the heart because heart reflects the Spirit.
So that’s why one.

46:30.650 --> 46:33.730
Then secondly we’ll have to put our hand
on the upper part of the abdomen on the left

46:33.730 --> 46:34.480
hand side. The whole thing we are working
out on the left hand side because here resides

46:34.480 --> 46:35.000
the center that governs the mastery. Then
below that is the center that governs the

46:35.000 --> 46:35.250
true knowledge, the pure knowledge.

46:35.170 --> 46:35.579
Then here is the center on the left hand side
which is very important, because this is the

46:35.579 --> 46:35.829
center where when we feel guilty, condemn
ourselves, try to show that we are sinners,

46:35.720 --> 46:35.970
we are good for nothing, a blocket is built
up. And that blocket is very common in the

46:35.890 --> 46:36.140
Western people, surprisingly. Whatever you
may say there is ego, this blocket of feeling

46:36.030 --> 46:36.280
guilty is too much. They all the time feel
guilty for everything that is nonsensical,

46:36.170 --> 46:36.420
or maybe little sensible also, but mostly
nonsensical. So a blocket is built. That’s

46:36.299 --> 46:36.549
how you develop this angina troubles and you
develop other troubles like spondylitis and

46:36.440 --> 46:36.690
all that. So this is a very important point.

46:36.520 --> 46:41.109
At the very outset you must know that you
are not guilty of anything, and God’s power

46:41.109 --> 46:42.619
of forgiveness is so great that He can wash
up whatever wrong you have done. He’s quite

46:42.619 --> 46:42.869
capable. So don’t try to condemn yourself.
Know that you are the temple of God and the

46:42.690 --> 46:42.940
Light has to come within you. That’s all.

46:42.809 --> 46:43.059
So the hand has to be here, push back when
I tell you. Then the hand goes here - is the

46:42.809 --> 46:43.059
center here is very important of Christ which
is in the center of optic chiasma. The center

46:42.809 --> 46:43.059
of Christ is there where you have to forgive
others. At the back is the center where you

46:42.809 --> 46:43.059
have to ask for forgiveness, just to get over
your guilt. And then you have to put your

46:42.950 --> 46:43.200
hand on top of the fontanel bone area which
is the soft bone in your childhood. Put your

46:43.079 --> 46:43.329
palm, just please put it just on top of that.
Stick out your fingers, press it hard and

46:43.079 --> 46:43.329
move it seven times clockwise when I tell
you.

46:43.079 --> 46:43.329
So this is what we have to do ultimately and
then you will see that the Cool Breeze will

46:43.079 --> 46:43.329
be coming out of this fontanel bone area.
You have to certify yourself and then you

46:43.079 --> 46:43.329
start feeling the All Pervading Power of God’s
Love as Cool Breeze around you, on your fingertips.

46:43.079 --> 46:43.329
You have to know on your fingertips. Nobody
else has to certify. You have to certify yourself.

46:43.079 --> 46:43.900
So now first of all we close our eyes. At
the very outset we have to tell ourselves

46:43.900 --> 46:44.289
that we are not guilty.

46:44.289 --> 46:45.059
[Shri Mataji speaks aside in Hindi] These
are uprooted people from India so you shouldn’t

46:45.059 --> 46:45.309
worry about them.

46:45.220 --> 46:46.039
Please have your right hand on your heart.
Keep your eyes shut. Please have your right

46:46.039 --> 46:48.039
hand on your heart. On the heart is on the
left hand side above the stomach. Heart. Higher,

46:48.039 --> 46:48.309
it’s higher. Now, at this point you have
to say, or you have to ask Me a question,

46:48.309 --> 46:48.559
in your heart.

46:48.359 --> 46:49.400
“Mother am I the Spirit?” Ask this question
three times. If you want you can call Me “Shri

46:49.400 --> 46:49.650
Mataji” or you can call Me “Mother”,
whatever suits you.

46:49.500 --> 46:49.750
“Mother am I the Spirit? Mother am I the
Spirit?” Ask the question three times.

46:49.670 --> 46:49.920
Now, put this right hand on the left hand
side in the upper part of your abdomen. Please

46:49.859 --> 46:50.109
put this right hand, your fingers, press them
in, on the left hand side, in the upper part

46:50.049 --> 46:50.299
of your abdomen, that is stomach. Now , this
is the center of the mastery. Keep your eyes

46:50.240 --> 46:50.490
shut. Now as you are the Spirit, you are your
own guide.

46:50.359 --> 46:50.609
So now ask the second question, “Mother,
am I my own master?” Three times. “Mother,

46:50.530 --> 46:50.780
am I my own guide?” “Mother, am I my own
guru?” Ask a question within yourselves.

46:50.700 --> 46:50.950
Three times.

46:50.720 --> 46:50.970
After asking this question please don’t
open your eyes, and put your right hand – left

46:50.880 --> 46:52.589
hand to be all the time towards Me and the
right hand in the lower part of your abdomen

46:52.589 --> 46:52.920
on the left hand side. Please put your right
hand in the lower part of your abdomen, your

46:52.920 --> 46:54.339
stomach, on the left side, on the left side.
Press it hard.

46:54.339 --> 46:54.589
Now this is the center of our true knowledge.
As I told you, you are free, I cannot force

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
things upon you. So please, you have to ask
for it. The true knowledge of Divine Power,

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
how it works, here you have to ask six times,
“Mother, please may I have the true knowledge,

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
the true technique? May I have the pure knowledge?”
Ask the question six times, please.

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
Keep your eyes shut, please. Don’t open
your eyes. Ask this question with full confidence,

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
please. Keep your eyes shut, please, all of
you.

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
Now, with your asking the Kundalini starts
getting alert. The Power of Desire wants to

46:54.589 --> 46:54.839
ascend. So you have to make proper seats or
arrangements for the Kundalini’s rise. So

46:54.589 --> 46:54.940
what do you do is to put your hand now on
the upper center that is placed on the left

46:54.940 --> 46:55.190
hand side of your abdomen, in the upper part.
Now, in the upper part of your stomach, on

46:55.000 --> 46:55.250
the left hand side you place your fingers.
Now press them.

46:55.030 --> 46:55.280
Now here you have to say with full confidence,
that the Kundalini wants to rise but you show

46:55.089 --> 46:55.339
your full confidence by saying ten times,
because this center has got ten petals, ten

46:55.140 --> 46:55.390
times. “Mother, I am my master. Mother,
I am my guide. Mother, I am my own guru.”

46:55.190 --> 46:55.440
Please say it with full confidence.

46:55.210 --> 46:55.460
This is the place is created by all the great
masters, satgurus as they are called, within

46:55.260 --> 46:55.510
us. They have to be awakened by this confidence
that you say. Ah. Ten times, please.

46:55.319 --> 46:55.569
[Shri Mataji rubs Her hands together and blows
on Her palms]

46:55.349 --> 46:55.599
Now raise your right hand on to your heart.
On the left hand side it is. Please raise

46:55.410 --> 46:55.660
your right hand on to your heart. Now here,
with full confidence again in yourself, you

46:55.460 --> 46:55.710
have to say, “Mother, I am the Spirit.”
Twelve times. “Mother, I am the Spirit.”

46:55.510 --> 46:55.760
Twelve times. “Mother, I am the Spirit.”
Twelve times. Because you are, but have confidence.

46:55.549 --> 46:55.799
Don’t feel guilty.

46:55.559 --> 46:55.809
As I told you, God is the Ocean of Love. He’s
the Ocean of Compassion, but above all He’s

46:55.619 --> 46:55.869
the Ocean of Forgiveness. With full confidence,
please say, “Mother I am the Spirit” twelve

46:55.670 --> 46:55.920
times.

46:55.670 --> 46:55.920
Now, with full confidence again, put your
hand on your neck on the left hand side from

46:55.730 --> 46:55.980
the front, from the front. Don’t take it
backwards because is easier from the front.

46:55.780 --> 46:56.030
And push it towards the back. Hold it tight,
hold it tight. Here is the problem where you

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
have to know that you are not guilty at all.
Here with full confidence please say sixteen

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
times, “Mother, I am not guilty.” Please
say it sixteen times with full confidence

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
in Me, yourself. You’re not guilty at all.
Believe Me, you’re not guilty of anything

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
– is all conditionings and all kinds of
things, the norms that people have created,

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
is all their mental projections. You’re
not guilty at all. Believe Me. But if you

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
still think you are guilty, you better have
punishment of saying it hundred and eight

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
times.

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
You have to be pleasantly placed because you
have to enter into the Kingdom of God. You

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
have to be pleasant about it. Not to be disgusted.
Now, sixteen times please say, “Mother,

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
I am not guilty at all.” Believe Me you
are not guilty.

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
From your heart please say, “I am not guilty.”
Believe Me. Believe Me.

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
Now, now raise your hand to your forehead
across and press it on both the sides as we

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
do when we have headaches. Now here you have
to say from your heart, from your heart, “Mother,

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
I forgive everyone.” But this is from your
heart. How many times is not the point.

46:56.000 --> 46:56.250
Now some people say that’s difficult to
forgive. But it is again a mental idea that

46:56.210 --> 46:56.460
we forgive someone, or we don’t forgive
someone. Actually, we don’t do anything.

46:56.250 --> 46:56.500
But when we don’t forgive, then we play
into the hands of people who want to do us

46:56.309 --> 46:56.559
harm.

46:56.309 --> 46:56.559
So put your hand on top of your forehead across,
forehead across and say, “Mother, I forgive

46:56.369 --> 46:56.619
everyone” from your heart. Please say it.
You wanted to have your Realization, isn’t

46:56.410 --> 46:56.660
it? Please, go ahead with it. Otherwise then
you’ll say “We didn’t feel it.” Come

46:56.460 --> 46:56.710
along. As you asked the question, please go
ahead. Everybody’s doing it. What’s so

46:56.500 --> 46:56.750
special about you? Just do it. Otherwise you’ll
say, “We didn’t get Realization.” Then

46:56.549 --> 46:56.799
I’m not responsible. You are here to get
your Realization. Be sensible. What are you

46:56.589 --> 46:56.839
going to lose?

46:56.599 --> 46:56.849
If you are seekers, please do it. [Shri Mataji
rubs Her hands together] It’s not proper

46:56.650 --> 46:56.900
that you should watch others. It’s not civil.

46:56.680 --> 46:56.930
Now put your hand on top of your head. Here
– we have missed one center because I don’t

46:56.740 --> 46:56.990
think you need to do that one where you have
to ask for forgiveness – but just put your

46:56.789 --> 46:57.039
hand on top of your head and press it hard
on the fontanel bone area and move it in a

46:56.859 --> 46:57.109
clockwise manner. Here now, again, I cannot
cross your freedom, so you have to say, “Mother,

46:56.910 --> 46:57.160
please give me my Realization.” Seven times.
“Please give me my Realization, I want it.”

46:56.960 --> 46:57.210
I cannot force it.

46:56.970 --> 46:57.220
Place your hand on top of your head, top of
your head, on the top, and press it hard,

46:57.030 --> 46:57.280
and move it. Now, seven times. Now, bring
down your hand, please. Slowly open your eyes.

46:57.079 --> 46:57.329
Slowly open your eyes. Now see, there are
no thoughts in the mind. Just see for yourself.

46:57.130 --> 46:57.380
Watch Me without any thought. Just watch Me.

46:57.160 --> 46:57.410
Put your left hand on top of your head. Left
hand. And right hand towards Me, and see if

46:57.220 --> 46:57.470
there’s a Cool Breeze coming in. Just move
it up and down. It’s very subtle. Here,

46:57.270 --> 46:57.520
here. Here, the fontanel bone is here. All
right? It’s very subtle.

46:57.309 --> 46:57.559
Now, change your hand. Put your left hand
towards Me. See with the right hand. [Shri

46:57.359 --> 46:57.609
Mataji blows into the microphone]

46:57.369 --> 46:57.619
Now change, see it with the other hand. Carefully.
